✨ Overview

A modern, multi-page web project demonstrating:

🌐 Responsive Design – Adaptive layouts for mobile, tablet, and desktop

🧠 Interactive Quiz – Multiple-choice quiz with scoring

🌤️ Professional Weather App – Live city weather info (temperature, wind, humidity, condition)

Built with HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript, featuring a professional color palette, subtle animations, and elegant glass effects.

🛠️ Features
1️⃣ Responsive Design

Elegant cards that adapt to all screen sizes using Flexbox & media queries

Smooth hover effects with subtle shadows

Gradient backgrounds and readable typography

2️⃣ Interactive Quiz

Instant feedback and score display 🎯

Clean, modern button styles with hover effects

3️⃣ Professional Weather App

Fetches live weather data for any city using the wttr.in API

Text-only output for a minimal and professional look

Clean layout with subtle animations
